---
// Video section for Academia Ewaffle
---

<section id="video" class="py-20 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Video Content -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <iframe 
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NK_4MupR8eQ?rel=0&modestbranding=1"
              title="Academia Ewaffle - Presentación"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
              allowfullscreen
              class="w-full h-full border-0"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Play Button Overlay -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white/90 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <i class="ri-play-fill text-3xl text-purple-600"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating Elements -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-yellow/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <i class="ri-video-line mr-2"></i>
          Conoce más sobre nosotros
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          Descubre cómo transformamos la educación digital
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          En este video te contamos cómo nació Academia Ewaffle y cómo hemos ayudado a cientos de profesionales 
          a crear contenido educativo de alta calidad usando las mejores herramientas del mercado.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Metodología probada y resultados comprobados</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Herramientas actualizadas y tendencias del mercado</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Comunidad activa de profesionales</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <a 
            href="#cursos"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-800 text-white rounded-full font-semibold hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-purple-900 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <i class="ri-arrow-right-line mr-2"></i>
            Ver cursos disponibles
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 